湯ﾙ@cbcd4cad438c814786cb9faa4022cf54f62c44a22f7811e0423f09694d392f27ﾚTitle: This week in Nushell #251
Path: Nushell
Content:
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13120] fixed deltas not being merged when evaluating menus
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13107] extended functionality of tango benchmark helpers
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13102] refactored Span ID (Step 2): Use SpanId of expressions in some places
.
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13116] improved performance of 
``explore``
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13130] updated uutils crates
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13122] added 
``$nu.data-dir``
 for completions and 
``$nu.cache-dir``
 for other uses
.
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13125] made the 
``which-support``
 feature non-optional
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13124] removed the deprecated 
``--not``
 flag on 
``str contains``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13114] removed old 
``sys``
 command behavior
, and made changes to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13007] how 
``path type``
 handles errors and missing files
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13146] expanded tables in help examples in std
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13145] added search terms to 
``if``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13138] fixed help for 
``banner``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13123] fixed multiple issues with 
``def --wrapped``
 help example
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13112] deprecated 
``--numbered``
 from 
``for``
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13097] allowed the addition of an index column to be optional for dataframes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13096] fixed the use of right-hand expressions in dataframe operations
.
hqsz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13110] fixed wrong casting with 
``into filesize``
.
壷@1e791254e152a534533367fe425c7f0635e196a8fc3e575d8f1a6e658eb7f8f6ﾚ亻itle: This week in Nushell #251
Path: Documentation
Content:
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1445] created a cookbook - new section on handling keypress loops using 
``input listen``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1439] linked from 'TiN -> Immutable Variables' to Variables chapter to reduce redundancy
.
gar1t 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1444] replaced 
``exit``
 with 
``dexit``
 for popd analog
.
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1443] added C toolchain to Ubuntu install instructions
.
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1440] removed feature from front matter and commands page
.
壷@5d743ed34cd3b0f8258b0a37325936784e044b0eb3bcdc11af7a09d0d182c0c0ﾚ_Title: This week in Nushell #251
Path: Nu_Scripts
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/879] updated the nu_msvs module
.
laisnuto 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/878] fixed an alert in kw completions
.
OJarrisonn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/877] added completions for 
``kw``
.
